title: Preview New alt-J Song “3ww” In LP3 Teaser
text: Other than a live album last summer, the knotty and inventive British art-prog combo alt-J haven't released anything since 2014 sophomore LP This Is All Yours . That appears to be changing imminently. The band just uploaded a teaser video featuring a minute of new music, which according to Shazam is the title track from … More »
